creator: utrading.io
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the world-class crypto trading robot. uTrading offers many types of trading robots and they are free to use! The robots created by uTrading run on cloud servers and can automatically execute your transactions around the clock without missing any trading opportunities.

✔ Complex transactions made simple
Using uTrading allows you to trade crypto like a professional, and complex crypto asset transactions will become simple from now on. Our servers are located near exchanges to ensure stable and fast order execution. Let trading robots assist you in executing your strategies without having to keep an eye on the market all the time.

✔ Everyone can quickly get started with uTrading robots
uTrading, trading for you, complex crypto transactions will become simple. Start your trading robot in 2 minutes, make money before learning. The robot offers manual and AI modes. In AI mode, the strategy parameters are optimized in real time according to the market.

✔ uTrading supports more than 200 digital currencies
Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC), Dogecoin (DOGE), Cardano (ADA), TRON (TRX), etc., you can use robot trading on uTrading.

✔ Free cryptocurrency trading bot
We do not charge software usage fees or membership fees, and all spot robots are free.

✔ Provide quantitative trading services for users of mainstream exchanges
Currently, it has established partnerships with Binance, OKX, Bybit, and Huobi to support spot and futures trading. Soon we will establish cooperation with KuCoin, Coinbase, Kraken, Gate.io, Bitget, Bitfinex.

✔ uTrading puts the safety of your assets first
uTrading has your security in mind from day one. Each API key is securely encrypted and stored using a FIPS 140-2 validated hardware security module (HSM) to protect the confidentiality and integrity of exchanged API keys. Your trading funds are safely stored in the exchange, uTrading only needs the ability to read data and conduct transactions, so uTrading cannot withdraw your funds from the exchange. At the same time, your uTrading account is also protected by multiple protections, including email verification login, Google two-step authenticator and your personal password.

Welcome to the world-class trading robot. The robots created by uTrading run on cloud servers and can automatically execute your transactions around the clock without missing any trading opportunities.

✔ Complex transactions made simple
Using uTrading allows you to trade like a professional, and complex asset transactions will become simple from now on. Our servers are located near exchanges to ensure stable and fast order execution. Let trading robots assist you in executing your strategies without having to keep an eye on the market all the time.

✔ Everyone can quickly get started with uTrading robots
uTrading, trading for you, complex transactions will become simple. Start your trading robot in 2 minutes, make money before learning. The robot offers manual and AI modes. In AI mode, the strategy parameters are optimized in real time according to the market.

✔ uTrading puts the safety of your assets first
uTrading has your security in mind from day one. Each API key is securely encrypted and stored using a FIPS 140-2 validated hardware security module (HSM) to protect the confidentiality and integrity of exchanged API keys. Your trading funds are safely stored in the exchange, uTrading only needs the ability to read data and conduct transactions, so uTrading cannot withdraw your funds from the exchange. At the same time, your uTrading account is also protected by multiple protections, including email verification login, Google two-step authenticator and your personal password.
